(2) The Board may— (a) accept moneys by way of grants or donations from any source in Zambia and, subject to the approval of the Minister, from any source outside Zambia; (b) subject to the approval of the Minister, raise by way of loans or otherwise such moneys as it may require for the discharge of its functions; (c) charge and collect fees in respect of programmes, seminars, consultancy services, and other services provided by the Board .
