(3) There shall be paid from the funds of the Board — (a) the salaries and allowances of the staff of the Board ; (b) such reasonable travelling, transport and subsistence allowances of members of the Board or of any committee when engaged on the business of the Board as the Board may determine; (c) any other expenses incurred by the Board in the discharge of its functions.
